Who: Lord Elder
Location: The Ark's command center

Lord Elder looked over curiously at Kup as Tuscon completed his
communcation, his face somewhat confused and worried. "Was it is just
me or did Tuscon sound a bit flustered?"

Elder does a quick sensor reading, and after a few moments the sensors
track Tuscon's last radio communication as comming from the area in or
around the old Maximal base.

It was only then that Lord Elder heard the screeching of tires over
the com signal that suddenly cut out.

"Lord Perseus, Tuscon, do you require assistance there?" Lord Elder
said, obviously misreading the whole situation.

(TAG)

Preston
